This course involves many sections to learn Python from zero to advanced.
You can find here what you can use to code in Python and there the parts such as Introduction to programming and Python, basics of Python, Advanced learning Python language and OOP.
You will find practical sessions more than the treories and documentations, you will learn Python by practicing and googling more on your own. 
After finishing this whole Python practicing, you will find the plan for learning Telegram bot, API, Backend Django and Data Science, Machine Learning on Python.
